Spending behavior

Customer preferences

🔍 Key Insights
📈 Total Revenue: 16.6M from ~45K orders

💰 Gross Profit: 6.1M (36.9%)

🧾 Net Profit: 2.1M (13%)

🍕 Top 5 products contributed ~74% of revenue

🔁 Repeat customers generated ~99% of revenue

📅 Weekdays contributed 71% of revenue

⚖️ Active & Seasonal products performed almost equally

⚠️ Some products consistently underperformed

💡 Business Recommendations
Improve low-performing products via:

Marketing strategies

Bundling offers

Pricing optimization

Invest more in high-performing products

Introduce customer loyalty programs

Optimize inventory based on seasonal demand

Track KPIs regularly for continuous improvement

